0:10:23.16,000 --> 0:10:26,000
I used the needle which has got a slight blade on the end.

193
0:10:26.16,000 --> 0:10:28,000
Can anybody see the blade on the end of that needle?

194
0:10:28.16,000 --> 0:10:3,000
Audience: No.

