226
0:12:01.16,000 --> 0:12:03,000
Even though they get on our nerves,

227
0:12:03.16,000 --> 0:12:05,000
I would never kill an insect

228
0:12:05.16,000 --> 0:12:09,000
because, "All creatures great and small" --

229
0:12:09.16,000 --> 0:12:11,000
there is a hymn that says that.

230
0:12:11.16,000 --> 0:12:14,000
So what I decided to do

231
0:12:14.16,000 --> 0:12:18,000
is to pluck fine hair out of my face.

232
0:12:18.16,000 --> 0:12:22,000
And I looked at it underneath the microscope.

